DATA CLOUD
Marketing Cloud Engagement Data Bundle Information

When ingesting data from Marketing Cloud Engagement, Data Cloud creates data streams and data lake objects (DLOs) for each starter bundle, along with schema and mappings to data model objects (DMOs).

Marketing Cloud Engagement starter data bundle data streams are grouped in data types: campaigns and journeys, contact, or engagement data. Learn about the created data streams, their associated bundles and categories, and links to mapping reference documentation.

TYPE, DESCRIPTION, AND REFERENCE	DATA STREAM	BUNDLE	CATEGORY


Campaigns and Journeys

These data streams relate to campaign and journey data associated with Marketing Cloud Engagement.

Marketing Cloud Engagement: Campaigns and Journeys

	SFMC Campaign	Email, WhatsApp	Other
SFMC Email Publication	Email	Other
SFMC Email Template	Email	Other
SFMC Journey	Email, WhatsApp	Other
SFMC Journey Activity	Email, WhatsApp	Profile
SFMC Push Template	MobilePush	Other
SFMC SMS Template	MobileConnect, WhatsApp	Other
SFMC WhatsApp Message Template	WhatsApp	Other


Contact

These data streams relate to contact data found in Marketing Cloud Engagement.

Marketing Cloud Engagement: Contact Mappings

	SFMC Contact Point App	MobilePush	Profile
SFMC Contact Point Email	Email	Profile
SFMC Contact Point Phone	MobileConnect, WhatsApp	Profile
SFMC Contact Point WhatsApp	WhatsApp	Profile
SFMC Subscriber	Email, WhatsApp	Profile


Engagement

These data streams relate to engagement data found in Marketing Cloud Engagement.

Marketing Cloud Engagement: Engagement Mappings

	SFMC EES Email Snapshot	Email	Other
SFMC EES Push Snapshot	MobilePush	Other
SFMC Einstein Email Scores	Email, MobilePush	Insights
SFMC Email Complaint	Email	Engagement
SFMC Email Engagement Bounce	Email	Engagement
SFMC Email Engagement Click	Email	Engagement

SFMC Email Engagement Send	Email	Engagement
SFMC Email Unsubscribe	Email	Engagement
SFMC Msg Engagement Event	MobileConnect, WhatsApp	Engagement

SFMC Push Undeliver Event	MobilePush	Engagement
SFMC WhatsApp MO Event	WhatsApp	Engagement
SFMC WhatsApp Send Event	WhatsApp	Engagement
SFMC WhatsApp Tracking Event	WhatsApp	Engagement
